items.badge_description: Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 95 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 20!

items.checkin_comment: Smooth Stout with coffee notes. Nitro pour gives a creamy head. Somewhat thin but an acceptable drop.

beer.beer_description: Under starry skies, hot coffee and porridge fuel the way. You step out into the darkness; it is here depth of character is found. This is an intriguing stout with layers deeper than most, it demands contemplation. Inspired by adventures in the Southern Alps

items.badge_description:
Thank you for celebrating International Stout Day by savoring a delicious stout! Stout enthusiasts like you know that there's a world of flavor waiting to be explored within the stout family, from classic dry stouts to rich barrel-aged stouts, and everything in between. Here's a toast to the deep, complex, and delightful world of stouts!

Keep exploring the rich, roasted flavors and aromatic notes that stouts have to offer, and earn other great stout badges like Beyond a Shadow of a Stout, Heavy Weight, Dessert Time! and more.

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 145 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 30!

Right about now youre feeling your face tighten and your taste buds explode. The full pucker is quickly setting in and you cant get enough. This is the wonder of the sour. That's 120 different Sour Beers. Try 5 more for Level 25.
Its been a long day and now its time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 90 different fruited beers. Try 5 more for Level 19!
